    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/e43994a4b7d793c17f8cf54b05213f4e.avif?t=1721186555\" width=480 height=90 /></span><br><br><i>MARGO - On the Brink</i> is a Turn-based RPG with roguelite/deckbuilding elements. Play as a nameless girl trapped deep inside the crumbling realities called &quot;The Brink&quot; and guide her to the truth of the sundered world. It will not be an easy journey as the hostile entities called &quot;Watchers&quot; are patrolling the ground. Draw strength from the benevolent beings called &quot;Whispers&quot; to stand up against the Watchers and find the long lost truth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/b9cb57a806b493e655d10131f595c236.avif?t=1721186555\" width=480 height=90 /></span><br><br>In MARGO, resource management is critical. Instead of a traditional levelling system, progression is tied to the ‘Whispers’ in your party. Each Whisper has its own specialization, such as healing or defending in the form of program cards. The program cards are single-use spells/skills and have their own EXP/Level progression. The more you use them, the stronger they will become. Even after a ‘Game Over,’ the cards will slowly get stronger in every subsequence retry! Recruit all the Lost Whispers and collect all 100+ cards!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/6a4c6856b9767c1435f3d323f8a5cf58.poster.avif?t=1721186555\" width=450 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/6a4c6856b9767c1435f3d323f8a5cf58.webm?t=1721186555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/6a4c6856b9767c1435f3d323f8a5cf58.mp4?t=1721186555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dive into the ever-changing realities of the Brink and reach for the truth. Secrets and surprises await you in every randomized cycles as you journey deeper into the sundered world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/383745e03ffad12eeefee69104e118e4.poster.avif?t=1721186555\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/383745e03ffad12eeefee69104e118e4.webm?t=1721186555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180930/extras/383745e03ffad12eeefee69104e118e4.mp4?t=1721186555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
